edberg_vail/abstracts/ndx_elsinger.pdf\n|display-authors=etal}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"engineerlive\">{{Cite web\n| title = Simplify hydrocarbon allocation and production reporting\n| accessdate = 2013-06-23\n| url = http://www.engineerlive.com/content/22347\n| publisher = Engineer Live\n}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"eubanks\">Larry S. Eubanks [http://lawlibrary.unm.edu/nrj/27/1/13_eubanks_unitization.pdf Review of book: Unitization of oil and gas fields in Texas]{{Dead link|date=October 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} Natural Resources Journal, Vol 27</ref>\n*<ref name=\"Warner2007\">{{cite book|author=Charles Albert Warner|title=Texas Oil and Gas Since 1543|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9cO8wnaDXIkC|accessdate=2013-06-23|date=May 2007|publisher=Copano Bay Press|isbn=978-0-9767799-5-7|page=163}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"johnson\">{{Cite book\n| title = The business of oil production\n| authors = Roswell Hill Johnson; Louis Grow Huntley; Ransom Evarts Somers\n| publisher = New York, Wiley\n| year = 1922\n| accessdate = 2013-06-23\n| page = 62\n| url = https://archive.org/stream/businessofoilpro00john#page/62/mode/2up\n}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"cramer\">{{Cite journal\n| authors = R. Cramer and D. Schotanus, Shell Global Solutions; K. Ibrahim, Brune Shell Petroleum; and N. Colbeck, Hess Corporation\n| title = Improving Allocation and Hydrocarbon Accounting Accuracy Using New Techniques\n| accessdate = 2013-06-23\n| date = October 2011\n| journal = SPE Economics & Management\n| volume = 4\n| number = 4\n| pages = 235\u2013240\n| url = http://www.onepetro.org/mslib/servlet/onepetropreview?id=SPE-125178-PA\n}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"cramer2009\">{{Cite web\n| title = Continuous well-flow estimates improve production allocation\n| accessdate = 2013-06-23\n|author1=Ron Cramer |author2=Dave Schotanus |author3=Kolin Ibrahim |author4=Nick Colbeck | date = 21 Dec 2009\n| url = http://www.ogj.com/articles/print/volume-107/issue-47/drilling-__production/continuous-well-flow.html\n}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"bazan\">{{Cite conference\n| publisher = Society of Petroleum Engineers\n| doi = 10.2118/40032-MS\n| isbn = 9781555633912\n| last = Bazan\n| first = L.W.\n| title = The Allocation of Gas Well Production Data Using Isotope Analysis\n| accessdate = 2013-06-23\n| date = March 1998\n| url = http://www.onepetro.org/mslib/app/Preview.do?paperNumber=00040032&societyCode=SPE\n}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"Nouvelle\">{{Cite conference\n| publisher = Society of Petroleum Engineers\n| doi = 10.2118/160812-MS\n| isbn = 9781613992173\n| last = Nouvelle\n| first = Xavier\n|author2=Katherine Rojas |author3=Artur Stankiewicz\n | title = Novel Method of Production Back-Allocation Using Geochemical Fingerprinting\n| accessdate = 2013-06-23\n| date = November 2012\n| url = http://www.onepetro.org/mslib/app/Preview.do?paperNumber=SPE-160812-MS&societyCode=SPE\n}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"cnlopb\">{{citation\n |publisher = Newfoundland and Labrador and Nova Scotia Offshore Areas, Drilling and Production Regulations\n |url       = http://www.cnlopb.nl.ca/pdfs/guidelines/meagl03.pdf\n |title     = Measurement Guidelines\n |isbn      = 978-1-927098-05-9\n |date      = September 2011\n}}{{Dead link|date=October 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"sapprodalloc\">{{Cite web\n| title = Primary Product Allocation Processing (SAP Library - SAP Oil & Gas (PRA - Production and Revenue Accounting))\n| accessdate = 2013-06-23\n| url = http://help.sap.com/saphelp_rc10/helpdata/en/27/1fff38911e924ce10000000a11405a/content.htm\n}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"oilgovern146\">{{cite book|author1=David G. Victor|author2=David R. Hults|author3=Mark C. Thurber|title=Oil and Governance: State-Owned Enterprises and the World Energy Supply|page=146|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pBuV5z_hnngC|accessdate=2013-06-23|date=8 December 2011|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-139-50288-7}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"oilgovern151\">Victor, D. G. et al (2011), p. 151</ref>\n*<ref name=\"WrigthGallun2005\">{{cite book|author1=Charlotte J. Wright |author2=Rebecca A. Gallun|title=International petroleum accounting|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=93xtSaC6EGIC|accessdate=2013-06-23|year=2005|publisher=PennWell Books|isbn=978-1-59370-016-4}}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"WrightGallun2005P237\">based on Wright & Gallun (2005), p. 237-238</ref>\n*<ref name=\"fl\u00f8lo\">Dag Hendrik Fl\u00f8lo ''Metering - NTNU, November 8, 2010.'' Based on a lecture at [[Norwegian University of Science and Technology]].</ref>\n*<ref name=\"Parshall\">Joel Parshall, [http://www.spe.org/jpt/print/archives/2009/09/11NewFieldDev.pdf \"Brazil Parque das Conchas Project Sets Subsea Separation, Pumping Milestone\"], ''Journal of Petroleum Technology'', September 2009, p.38&ndash;42.</ref> \n*<ref name=\"ercb\">\nInspired by drawings in:<BR /> {{Cite book\n| publisher = ERCB\n| authors = Energy Resources Conservation Board, Alberta, Canada\n| title = Measurement requirements for oil and gas operations\n| location = Calgary\n| year = 2013\n| pages = 4\u20138\n| url = http://www.aer.ca/rules-and-regulations/directives/directive-017\n| access-date = 2013-06-29\n| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130825113347/http://www.aer.ca/rules-and-regulations/directives/directive-017\n| archive-date = 2013-08-25\n| url-status=dead\n| df = \n}}\n</ref>\n* <ref name=\"Mccaffrey\">{{Cite journal\n| pages = 55\u201359\n| authors = Mark A. Mccaffrey, David K. Baskin and Brooks A. Patterson, Weatherford \n| title = Oil fingerprinting dramatically reduces production allocation costs\n| journal = World Oil\n| date = March 2012\n}} available at [http://www.weatherford.com/weatherford/groups/web/documents/weatherfordcorp/wft194606.pdf weatherford.com] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130207103254/http://weatherford.com/weatherford/groups/web/documents/weatherfordcorp/wft194606.pdf |date=2013-02-07 }}</ref>\n*<ref name=\"larsen\">{{Cite web\n| title = Online 